      of the Paragraph.
    </h1>
    <button onclick="change()">Click Me</button>

    <script>
      function change() {
        document.getElementById("para").innerHTML =
          "Hey There ! This paragraph changed due to a click on this button. Event Listener changes the details when an event id placed.";
      }
    </script>
